screenButtonsHelpText.value: Explore solution concentration with solutes in water.

playArea.value: A solute dispenser and water faucet sit above a drainable beaker. Choose from a variety of solutes to dispense one at a time, in either solid or solution form. On the right is a concentration meter with movable probe. On the bottom is a slider to control evaporation, and a button to remove solute from the solution.
